20:39.150 --> 20:40.500
It was weaponized
by the Russians

20:40.543 --> 20:41.979
during the last election.

20:42.023 --> 20:44.243
They could target
their fake news articles

20:44.286 --> 20:46.201
towards smaller
and smaller groups.

20:46.245 --> 20:48.812
You're saying this was used
against our jurors?

20:48.856 --> 20:50.292
Yep, through
their Facebook pages.

20:50.336 --> 20:52.773
And they can really
target just 12 people?

