to 58,000.

21:12.836 --> 21:15.317
He also subscribes
toThe New York Times.

21:15.361 --> 21:17.667
That narrows it down to

21:17.711 --> 21:19.669
1,489 men.

21:19.713 --> 21:21.367
So, you keep refining it

21:21.410 --> 21:24.021
down and down to a group
of 1,000 or so people,

21:24.065 --> 21:26.415
who you know will
include your jurors.

21:26.459 --> 21:28.330
How do we know this?

21:28.374 --> 21:30.332
