22:13.157 --> 22:14.985
No. It's all anonymous.

22:15.029 --> 22:16.770
He can create
a fictional news service

22:16.813 --> 22:18.337
with fictional articles,

22:18.380 --> 22:20.513
and we have no way
to know who did it.

22:22.428 --> 22:24.386
He's using those articles
to undercut us.

22:24.430 --> 22:26.388
So we show it to the judge.

22:26.432 --> 22:28.434
It doesn't matter
if it's anonymous.

22:28.477 --> 22:31.524
Clearly, Solomon is
the one who benefits.

22:31.567 --> 22:34.744
So, this is fake news?

22:34.788 --> 22:36.833
It's more than fake news,
Your Honor. It can lead to...

22:36.877 --> 22:38.400
Where did you get
your information, Mr. Waltzer?

22:38.444 --> 22:39.662
The dog fight?

22:39.706 --> 22:41.098
It is not just

22:41.142 --> 22:42.926
the dog fights, Your Honor.

22:42.970 --> 22:45.059
It's also the accusations
of perjury

22:45.102 --> 22:47.191
against our
expert witness.

22:47.235 --> 22:49.368
Again, Your Honor, I'd rather
not talk over everybody.

22:49.411 --> 22:51.152
Mr. Boseman,

22:51.195 --> 22:52.153
wait.

22:52.196 --> 22:53.502
Where did this come from?

22:53.546 --> 22:54.982
I don't know, Your Honor.

22:55.025 --> 22:57.201
Came from a paralegal,
and he's since been dismissed.

22:57.245 --> 22:58.551
This is bullshit.

22:58.594 --> 22:59.856
Stop.
I mean...

22:59.900 --> 23:03.120
So, what is your
requested remedy, a mistrial?

23:03.164 --> 23:06.776
No. The same tactic can be used
against a new jury.

23:06.820 --> 23:08.778
And you happen to like
this jury?

23:08.822 --> 23:10.563
That has nothing to do with it.

23:10.606 --> 23:11.651
Look, I can instruct the jury

23:11.694 --> 23:13.392
to, uh, ignore
its Facebook feed...

23:13.435 --> 23:15.785
Which will have the exact
opposite effect, Your Honor.

23:15.829 --> 23:18.658
The first thing they'll do is
go check their Facebook feeds.

23:18.701 --> 23:20.050
So you want me to ignore this?

23:20.094 --> 23:22.139
No, we ask that you
censure the defense

23:22.183 --> 23:23.445
for employing
these tactics.

23:23.489 --> 23:24.968
These are not
my tactics, Your Honor.

23:25.012 --> 23:26.622
I must admit to being

23:26.666 --> 23:28.102
a bit of a luddite.

23:28.145 --> 23:30.365
None of this Facebook business
makes much sense to me.

23:30.409 --> 23:32.498
Your Honor, one of the
microtargeted articles

23:32.541 --> 23:36.197
reports that our firm was
prosecuted for stealing money.

23:36.240 --> 23:38.286
And that I was prosecuted
for sexual harassment.

23:38.329 --> 23:40.897
I understand your outrage,
but we have no way

23:40.941 --> 23:42.725
to trace this back
to the defense.

23:42.769 --> 23:44.510
Then we ask that we be
allowed to question

23:44.553 --> 23:47.382
an I.T. specialist
on how microtargeting is used.

23:47.426 --> 23:48.601
I will instruct the jury
to ignore

23:48.644 --> 23:49.950
any references
to dog fights or perjury,

23:49.993 --> 23:52.996
but I will not bias them
against Mr. Waltzer.

23:53.040 --> 23:55.912
Now, can we please
have the jury come in?

23:55.956 --> 23:57.653
What about a mistrial?

23:57.697 --> 24:00.264
No. The jury likes
the ballistics.

24:00.308 --> 24:02.528
Let me try something.

24:02.571 --> 24:03.790
Jay.

24:12.538 --> 24:14.496
Solomon's acting
like an old fool,

24:14.540 --> 24:16.498
but he's the one behind
the microtargeting.

24:16.542 --> 24:20.154
Yeah, I agree.
What do you need?

24:20.197 --> 24:22.069
He's doing it
anonymously,

24:22.112 --> 24:25.333
so there's no way to
trace it back to him.

24:25.376 --> 24:27.466
Or to anybody.

24:29.511 --> 24:32.819
And this is not something
I can ask you to do, Jay.

24:32.862 --> 24:35.865
I can only
tell you...

24:35.909 --> 24:38.346
what I wish
would happen.

24:38.389 --> 24:40.261
I'm on it.

24:46.702 --> 24:48.835
What are you doing?

24:48.878 --> 24:50.489
Typing.

24:50.532 --> 24:54.144
Ah. Fictional
news service.

24:54.188 --> 24:56.582
Making fake news,
are we?

24:56.625 --> 24:59.976
So, are we writing something
about Solomon Waltzer?

25:00.020 --> 25:01.804
Caught with child porn
or something?

25:01.848 --> 25:04.459
Wearen't doing anything.

25:04.503 --> 25:07.288
Where are the
juror rundowns?

25:07.331 --> 25:10.987
Uh... right there.

25:28.875 --> 25:30.267
Jay Dipersia's phone.

