Someone in prison.

25:57.904 --> 26:00.036
Uh...

26:02.038 --> 26:03.997
Okay.

26:04.040 --> 26:05.476
I'll see what I can do.

26:14.877 --> 26:16.531
Who was that?

26:16.575 --> 26:18.185
