26:18.228 --> 26:20.143
He needs a lawyer?

26:20.187 --> 26:23.538
Uh-huh.

26:23.582 --> 26:26.062
If only we knew some.

26:26.106 --> 26:28.499
I'd rather have you
not tell anyone.

26:28.543 --> 26:30.763
Why?
This is my thing.

