27:00.575 --> 27:02.882
And you blame
Detective Whitehead?

27:02.925 --> 27:04.927
Yeah.

27:04.971 --> 27:07.669
That's why this accusation in
the civil case is so important.

27:07.713 --> 27:10.280
He's accused of using
drop guns in other cases.

27:10.324 --> 27:13.457
It's a civil case and it's just
a charge at this point,

27:13.501 --> 27:15.851
