get into trouble.

27:25.165 --> 27:27.297
No. Both cases help each other.

27:27.341 --> 27:30.039
Jay, you need
to tell the partners

27:30.083 --> 27:32.041
that's why you brought
Rashid's case to the firm.

27:32.085 --> 27:33.608
