27:53.584 --> 27:56.805
Okay.

27:56.849 --> 27:58.807
Look, we'll do
the best we can.

27:58.851 --> 28:00.461
We'll file an appeal

28:00.504 --> 28:02.115
and ask for the case
to be reopened

28:02.158 --> 28:03.551
based on new information.

28:03.594 --> 28:06.206
Thank you.

28:06.249 --> 28:09.731
Okay.

28:09.775 --> 28:12.691
So, we are going to have a trial
at some point, right?

28:12.734 --> 28:14.605
The defense is ready,
Your Honor,

28:14.649 --> 28:15.998
